    <measure>Proportion of participants achieving Hidradenitis Suppurativa Clinical Response (HiSCR)</measure>
    <time_frame>At Week 12</time_frame>
    <description>HiSCR defined as at least a 50% reduction in the AN count with no increase in abscess count and no increase in draining fistula count relative to Baseline.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
